nhc_headline: ...HENRIETTE PASSING FAR NORTHEAST OF THE HAWAIIAN ISLANDS...
summary: ...HENRIETTE PASSING FAR NORTHEAST OF THE HAWAIIAN ISLANDS... As of 11:00 PM HST Sat Aug 09 the center of Henriette was located near 23.8, -150.3 with movement NW at 15 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1006 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 40 mph.
